{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MzE0MQ_0004", "text": "如共你再錯失半步 便是我的盡頭", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 5, 4, 4, 3, 4, 2, 2, 2, 5, 3, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jyu4", "gung6", "nei5", "zoi3", "co3", "sat1", "bun3", "bou6", "bin6", "si6", "ngo5", "dik1", "zeon6", "tau4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "如共", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "再", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "錯失", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "半步", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "便是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "盡頭", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "孤獨探戈", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3141", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MzE0MQ_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MzE0MQ_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MzE0MQ_0005", "text": "明白沒有 在懸崖上哪可退後", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 2, 5, 2, 0, 0, 5, 9, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ming4", "baak6", "mut6", "jau5", "zoi6", "jyun4", "ngaai4", "naa5", "ho2", "teoi3", "hau6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "明白", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "懸崖", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "哪", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "可", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "退後", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "孤獨探戈", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3141", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MzE0MQ_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MzE0MQ_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
